1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 14]

2
00:00:26,381 --> 00:00:27,460
All these years,

3
00:00:28,381 --> 00:00:29,740
he's pushed you to the forefront,

4
00:00:32,381 --> 00:00:33,220
making it seem noble

5
00:00:33,221 --> 00:00:34,140
as if he were

6
00:00:34,141 --> 00:00:35,780
training the head of the Zhou family.

7
00:00:36,021 --> 00:00:36,900
But in reality,

8
00:00:38,061 --> 00:00:39,580
it's so that when problems arise,

9
00:00:39,581 --> 00:00:40,660
you can take the blame for him.

10
00:00:40,941 --> 00:00:42,140
But what does it matter?

11
00:00:43,701 --> 00:00:45,260
You may never understand

12
00:00:45,821 --> 00:00:46,980
that being used by my father

13
00:00:48,021 --> 00:00:49,260
is also my happiness

14
00:00:50,141 --> 00:00:51,060
and fulfillment.

15
00:00:56,901 --> 00:00:57,500
Fifth concubine.

16
00:01:00,621 --> 00:01:02,140
The outfit you're wearing today

17
00:01:03,821 --> 00:01:04,820
looks really nice.

18
00:01:06,381 --> 00:01:07,260
You chose it.

19
00:01:09,461 --> 00:01:10,260
Fifth concubine.

20
00:01:14,901 --> 00:01:16,180
shall meet again in the next life.

21
00:03:00,741 --> 00:03:01,700
In the end,

22
00:03:04,101 --> 00:03:05,100
he didn't betray Master Zhou.

23
00:03:16,501 --> 00:03:17,540
I told you the scent from Zhou Tea House

24
00:03:17,541 --> 00:03:19,180
hasn't been right for two years now.

25
00:03:19,381 --> 00:03:19,940
Who would have thought

26
00:03:19,941 --> 00:03:21,580
they were selling harmful opium paste.

27
00:03:21,661 --> 00:03:22,420
Never expected that!

28
00:03:22,541 --> 00:03:23,540
Fellow townspeople,

29
00:03:24,621 --> 00:03:25,340
this place

30
00:03:26,141 --> 00:03:27,420
may look like a restaurant,

31
00:03:27,941 --> 00:03:28,540
but actually

32
00:03:28,661 --> 00:03:30,620
it's Zhou Yichen's Opium smuggling warehouse.

33
00:03:30,821 --> 00:03:32,940
Before his death, he repented

34
00:03:33,061 --> 00:03:34,620
and confessed everything.

35
00:03:35,181 --> 00:03:36,540
My father is unwell,

36
00:03:36,821 --> 00:03:38,460
so I'm here to destroy it on his behalf.

37
00:03:38,581 --> 00:03:40,020
Thank heavens the eldest son of the Zhou family

38
00:03:40,021 --> 00:03:41,260
is an upright man.

39
00:03:41,381 --> 00:03:42,460
Yes, indeed!

40
00:03:42,461 --> 00:03:43,460
Thank goodness Young Master Zhou is here.

41
00:03:47,741 --> 00:03:49,020
So you knew all along

42
00:03:49,101 --> 00:03:50,220
that Master Zhou and Zhou Yichen

43
00:03:50,621 --> 00:03:51,980
were smuggling opium

44
00:03:52,141 --> 00:03:53,020
under the guise of buying and selling tea?

45
00:03:53,701 --> 00:03:54,340
Yes.

46
00:03:56,221 --> 00:03:57,580
No wonder the opium destruction hero

47
00:03:57,941 --> 00:03:59,380
could always locate

48
00:03:59,581 --> 00:04:01,340
and destroy smuggled opium quickly.

49
00:04:01,661 --> 00:04:02,580
This so-called hero

50
00:04:02,661 --> 00:04:03,660
is nothing but a mole.

51
00:04:04,661 --> 00:04:05,460
You can't deny the hero

52
00:04:05,461 --> 00:04:06,980
just because his father is bad,

53
00:04:06,981 --> 00:04:08,260
can you?

54
00:04:10,901 --> 00:04:12,380
What a well-played game.

55
00:04:12,541 --> 00:04:13,980
As long as no one is hurt,

56
00:04:14,221 --> 00:04:15,340
and no evil is done,

57
00:04:16,341 --> 00:04:17,780
what does it matter if some tactics are used?

58
00:04:22,981 --> 00:04:23,980
How could this happen?

59
00:04:24,821 --> 00:04:25,620
Yichen...

60
00:04:26,741 --> 00:04:29,180
Why would he reveal everything?

61
00:04:29,861 --> 00:04:30,980
I've also heard

62
00:04:31,501 --> 00:04:32,940
many merchants who already signed

63
00:04:32,941 --> 00:04:34,300
next year's orders with us

64
00:04:34,541 --> 00:04:35,700
have been lured to the He family.

65
00:04:36,061 --> 00:04:37,100
It's said that Master He

66
00:04:37,101 --> 00:04:38,580
offered them bigger discounts.

67
00:04:38,981 --> 00:04:41,380
Is there a mysterious leader at the He residence?

68
00:04:41,621 --> 00:04:42,500
I've heard rumors,

69
00:04:43,421 --> 00:04:46,220
but I've never seen anyone like that at the He residence.

70
00:04:46,301 --> 00:04:47,540
Grandma never mentioned it either.

71
00:04:49,901 --> 00:04:51,500
It's that Master He again.

72
00:04:52,701 --> 00:04:54,100
Have you found out his background?

73
00:04:54,221 --> 00:04:55,300
Not yet.

74
00:04:55,701 --> 00:04:56,780
I've only heard

75
00:04:56,781 --> 00:04:58,900
he invested in several banks outside:

76
00:04:59,341 --> 00:05:00,100
He acquired the largest textile

77
00:05:00,101 --> 00:05:01,980
and medicinal herb industries in Wu county.

78
00:05:02,101 --> 00:05:02,780
Rumors say

79
00:05:03,461 --> 00:05:04,700
this Master He

80
00:05:04,701 --> 00:05:06,260
is about your age,

81
00:05:06,781 --> 00:05:07,820
and among the common folk,

82
00:05:08,021 --> 00:05:10,340
he has an illegitimate daughter who remains unfound.

83
00:05:12,021 --> 00:05:13,340
Illegitimate daughter?

84
00:05:14,901 --> 00:05:16,100
Even if found,

85
00:05:16,581 --> 00:05:17,620
what trouble

86
00:05:18,261 --> 00:05:20,140
could a woman cause?

87
00:05:20,701 --> 00:05:21,780
At most, Yimo

88
00:05:21,781 --> 00:05:23,340
gains another sister.

89
00:05:24,221 --> 00:05:24,780
Yes.

90
00:05:25,461 --> 00:05:26,580
Absolutely, Master.

91
00:05:36,901 --> 00:05:38,700
Has Master been taking those medicines on time?

92
00:05:39,181 --> 00:05:40,020
All taken.

93
00:05:40,781 --> 00:05:41,420
Look,

94
00:05:41,781 --> 00:05:43,060
isn't that the third concubine?

95
00:05:48,301 --> 00:05:49,180
Go call for help...

96
00:05:49,181 --> 00:05:50,100
I'll wait here.

97
00:06:05,821 --> 00:06:06,700
Rescuing her is urgent!

98
00:06:11,661 --> 00:06:12,540
Third concubine!

99
00:06:13,901 --> 00:06:14,740
Third concubine!

100
00:06:26,541 --> 00:06:27,740
What's the matter, steward?

101
00:06:28,181 --> 00:06:29,060
Young master,

102
00:06:29,261 --> 00:06:31,460
Master wishes to dine with you tonight.

103
00:06:31,821 --> 00:06:32,580
The kitchen specially prepared

104
00:06:32,581 --> 00:06:34,340
several dishes you enjoy.

105
00:06:35,781 --> 00:06:36,580
Thank you, steward.

106
00:06:37,101 --> 00:06:37,620
Let's go.

107
00:06:42,341 --> 00:06:43,580
Where could she go?

108
00:06:47,781 --> 00:06:48,980
Aren't you the new maid

109
00:06:48,981 --> 00:06:50,100
from the fifth concubine's quarters?

110
00:06:50,581 --> 00:06:51,780
Why so nervous?

111
00:06:52,381 --> 00:06:52,660
I saw

112
00:06:52,661 --> 00:06:55,340
her enter the ancestral hall just now.

113
00:06:55,901 --> 00:06:56,660
Ancestral hall?

114
00:06:56,661 --> 00:06:58,100
It's pitch black inside,

115
00:06:58,221 --> 00:06:59,140
no lights on.

116
00:06:59,261 --> 00:07:00,260
I heard the fifth concubine

117
00:07:00,261 --> 00:07:01,700
crying for an hour.

118
00:07:02,261 --> 00:07:03,460
She seemed

119
00:07:03,461 --> 00:07:04,980
possessed or something.

120
00:07:05,101 --> 00:07:06,620
Young master, this might be a trap.

121
00:07:06,901 --> 00:07:07,780
Master awaits your presence.

122
00:07:07,781 --> 00:07:08,740
Don't lose sight of priorities.

123
00:07:12,821 --> 00:07:13,580
Are you certain?

124
00:07:14,501 --> 00:07:15,460
Absolutely certain.

125
00:07:15,781 --> 00:07:16,380
Young master,

126
00:07:16,381 --> 00:07:17,860
should we inform Master?

127
00:07:19,261 --> 00:07:20,340
Go tell my father

128
00:07:20,461 --> 00:07:22,260
I have an urgent conference call

129
00:07:22,261 --> 00:07:23,220
and will see him later.

130
00:07:23,501 --> 00:07:23,980
Young master...

131
00:07:26,141 --> 00:07:27,740
No one else must know of this.

132
00:07:28,221 --> 00:07:28,740
Understood.

133
00:07:28,741 --> 00:07:29,740
I warn you

134
00:07:29,741 --> 00:07:30,740
if anything goes wrong,

135
00:07:30,981 --> 00:07:32,580
your head may not stay attached.

136
00:07:32,981 --> 00:07:33,900
I understand.

137
00:07:40,621 --> 00:07:41,380
Fifth concubine?

138
00:07:42,501 --> 00:07:43,100
Fifth concubine?

139
00:07:43,621 --> 00:07:44,220
Fifth concubine?

140
00:07:44,861 --> 00:07:45,980
I'll take you away from here.

141
00:07:45,981 --> 00:07:47,660
It's a trap! Go quickly!

142
00:07:52,021 --> 00:07:53,420
What is this?

143
00:07:53,421 --> 00:07:55,700
It's a love potion.

144
00:08:24,301 --> 00:08:24,940
Feiyue!

145
00:08:26,141 --> 00:08:26,780
Where is Master?

146
00:08:26,781 --> 00:08:28,300
Aren't they supposed to dine together?

147
00:08:28,501 --> 00:08:29,820
The third concubine just dragged the master

148
00:08:29,821 --> 00:08:30,780
for a walk in the courtyard.

149
00:08:30,781 --> 00:08:32,780
Said the plum blossoms in the ancestral hall have bloomed.

150
00:08:32,781 --> 00:08:33,700
Ancestral hall?

151
00:08:51,981 --> 00:08:52,660
Love Potion.

152
00:08:56,221 --> 00:08:57,060
Zhou Yimo.

153
00:08:58,101 --> 00:08:58,900
Wake up!

154
00:09:00,021 --> 00:09:00,940
Wake up now!

155
00:09:08,421 --> 00:09:09,100
Zhou Yimo!

156
00:09:09,941 --> 00:09:10,940
Wake up quickly!

157
00:09:11,581 --> 00:09:12,740
It's Love Potion.

158
00:09:14,381 --> 00:09:15,940
I really want to be with you...

159
00:09:24,341 --> 00:09:26,420
Master, you look much better lately.

160
00:09:27,661 --> 00:09:28,460
"Never imagined Chen

161
00:09:28,541 --> 00:09:30,220
would leave before me.
- Hurry!

162
00:09:38,541 --> 00:09:39,300
Yimo!

163
00:09:40,701 --> 00:09:41,500
Father!

164
00:09:42,541 --> 00:09:43,060
You...

165
00:09:43,941 --> 00:09:45,900
What the hell are you doing, you bastards?

166
00:09:46,341 --> 00:09:47,060
Heavens!

167
00:09:47,421 --> 00:09:49,460
How dare you commit such immoral acts!

168
00:09:52,541 --> 00:09:53,300
Master!

169
00:09:54,341 --> 00:09:55,660
It's not what you think!

170
00:09:58,061 --> 00:09:58,820
Guards!

171
00:09:59,421 --> 00:10:00,300
Lock this woman

172
00:10:00,501 --> 00:10:01,820
in the cold courtyard!

173
00:10:01,941 --> 00:10:03,420
Execute her by hanging tomorrow!

174
00:10:03,421 --> 00:10:04,060
Yes!

175
00:10:05,301 --> 00:10:05,940
Move!

176
00:10:08,181 --> 00:10:10,220
Father, it's not what you think!

177
00:10:12,141 --> 00:10:14,340
I despise traitors most.

178
00:10:14,661 --> 00:10:16,300
I'll shoot you dead!

179
00:10:16,901 --> 00:10:18,700
Master, don't be impulsive!

180
00:10:18,781 --> 00:10:19,940
The second young master just died.

181
00:10:20,141 --> 00:10:21,900
This family can't take any more.

182
00:10:32,021 --> 00:10:32,860
Master.

183
00:10:42,981 --> 00:10:44,580
I'll give you three sentences.

184
00:10:45,541 --> 00:10:47,140
If you can't explain clearly,

185
00:10:48,581 --> 00:10:49,700
you'll die

186
00:10:50,061 --> 00:10:51,180
along with that woman!

187
00:10:53,581 --> 00:10:54,900
I just returned today

188
00:10:55,421 --> 00:10:57,620
when Lian'er told me Fifth Concubine was in trouble.

189
00:10:59,221 --> 00:11:00,540
When I rushed to the ancestral hall,

190
00:11:00,541 --> 00:11:02,500
she was already lying there disheveled.

191
00:11:03,381 --> 00:11:04,980
Then I was affected by Love Potion too.

192
00:11:05,501 --> 00:11:06,580
That's when you arrived, Father.

193
00:11:06,861 --> 00:11:07,580
Where's Lian'er?

194
00:11:08,141 --> 00:11:09,140
Waiting outside.

195
00:11:10,341 --> 00:11:11,180
Bring her in!

196
00:11:17,461 --> 00:11:18,060
Master.

197
00:11:18,581 --> 00:11:19,780
Isn't this too frightening?

198
00:11:19,901 --> 00:11:20,500
Speak!

199
00:11:21,221 --> 00:11:22,540
What exactly happened?

200
00:11:24,541 --> 00:11:25,260
Master,

201
00:11:25,781 --> 00:11:27,540
what do you want me to say?

202
00:11:28,061 --> 00:11:29,220
The young master says

203
00:11:29,461 --> 00:11:30,820
you told him Fifth Concubine

204
00:11:30,981 --> 00:11:32,340
was in trouble at the ancestral hall.

205
00:11:32,341 --> 00:11:33,300
That's why he went.

206
00:11:34,021 --> 00:11:35,220
Is this true?

207
00:11:37,381 --> 00:11:38,220
No.

208
00:11:40,621 --> 00:11:41,340
Today

209
00:11:41,501 --> 00:11:42,620
I never saw the young master.

210
00:11:42,621 --> 00:11:43,460
Bullshit!

211
00:11:44,621 --> 00:11:46,140
You clearly told me yourself!

212
00:11:46,861 --> 00:11:48,660
My driver Zhang Jinbao was there too.

213
00:11:49,581 --> 00:11:50,740
But everyone in the mansion

214
00:11:50,861 --> 00:11:51,740
knows

215
00:11:52,061 --> 00:11:53,700
Zhang Jinbao serves you.

216
00:11:54,621 --> 00:11:56,380
Naturally he'd cover up the lie for you.

217
00:11:56,981 --> 00:11:58,540
Who put you up to saying this?

218
00:11:59,141 --> 00:11:59,900
Third Concubine,

219
00:12:00,621 --> 00:12:01,860
why are you protecting her?

220
00:12:03,141 --> 00:12:04,060
I could never protect

221
00:12:04,061 --> 00:12:05,140
a maid.

222
00:12:05,981 --> 00:12:06,780
Young Master.

223
00:12:07,261 --> 00:12:08,620
When you returned home today

224
00:12:08,821 --> 00:12:10,140
the steward must have informed you

225
00:12:10,581 --> 00:12:12,180
that you were to dine with Master tonight.

226
00:12:12,621 --> 00:12:13,620
But the moment you entered

227
00:12:13,621 --> 00:12:14,980
you went straight to Fifth Concubine.

228
00:12:15,261 --> 00:12:16,780
Isn't that improper?

229
00:12:19,061 --> 00:12:19,700
What?

230
00:12:20,781 --> 00:12:22,780
Now you have nothing to say?

231
00:12:24,141 --> 00:12:24,660
Speak!

232
00:12:25,421 --> 00:12:27,260
What exactly did you go to her for?

233
00:12:27,581 --> 00:12:29,220
As Third Concubine put it,

234
00:12:30,141 --> 00:12:31,260
I have feelings for Fifth Concubine.

235
00:12:31,261 --> 00:12:31,860
Right?

236
00:12:32,061 --> 00:12:33,260
I never said that.

237
00:12:33,421 --> 00:12:34,420
Even if I were into that,

238
00:12:35,301 --> 00:12:36,420
if I had feelings for her,

239
00:12:36,741 --> 00:12:38,380
why wouldn't I meet her in my own room?

240
00:12:39,181 --> 00:12:40,300
Why forgo a proper bed

241
00:12:40,301 --> 00:12:41,700
to come to a place like the ancestral hall

242
00:12:41,701 --> 00:12:42,780
to engage in such filthy acts?

243
00:12:43,141 --> 00:12:43,940
Isn't that right, Father?

244
00:12:44,021 --> 00:12:44,940
How dare you!

245
00:12:45,981 --> 00:12:47,740
How could you utter

246
00:12:47,741 --> 00:12:49,180
such treacherous words!

247
00:12:49,181 --> 00:12:50,580
Who knows?

248
00:12:50,581 --> 00:12:51,700
Maybe you enjoy that sort of thing.

249
00:12:51,701 --> 00:12:52,540
Shut up!

250
00:12:53,701 --> 00:12:54,700
I spoke out of turn.

251
00:12:55,301 --> 00:12:56,660
Even if I am into that sort of thing,

252
00:12:57,741 --> 00:12:58,540
what about Fifth Concubine?

253
00:12:59,381 --> 00:13:00,540
If she was willing,

254
00:13:00,541 --> 00:13:01,980
why did she stab me with her hairpin?

255
00:13:03,261 --> 00:13:04,100
Who knows?

256
00:13:04,101 --> 00:13:05,780
Maybe it was all an act.

257
00:13:06,581 --> 00:13:07,220
Master,

258
00:13:07,301 --> 00:13:08,660
when we entered the room,

259
00:13:08,701 --> 00:13:10,300
Fifth Concubine was disheveled.

260
00:13:10,381 --> 00:13:11,620
If she truly resisted...

261
00:13:12,061 --> 00:13:12,820
Enough!

262
00:13:13,341 --> 00:13:14,460
No more!

263
00:13:14,861 --> 00:13:16,100
You're no longer to go to the docks.

264
00:13:17,341 --> 00:13:17,980
Guards!

265
00:13:18,581 --> 00:13:19,660
Lock him up!

266
00:13:20,021 --> 00:13:21,420
No food for three days!

267
00:13:21,981 --> 00:13:22,660
Young Master

268
00:13:23,021 --> 00:13:23,740
if you please!

269
00:13:23,741 --> 00:13:24,380
Father,

270
00:13:24,981 --> 00:13:25,620
Fifth Concubine...

271
00:13:25,661 --> 00:13:26,940
Whether she was willing or not

272
00:13:28,861 --> 00:13:30,140
no longer matters.

273
00:13:31,181 --> 00:13:32,020
Tomorrow,

274
00:13:32,541 --> 00:13:33,460
hang her.

275
00:13:35,581 --> 00:13:36,220
Father!

276
00:13:37,941 --> 00:13:38,580
Father!

277
00:13:40,581 --> 00:13:41,420
Master,

278
00:13:41,701 --> 00:13:43,860
may I return to my duties now?

279
00:13:46,141 --> 00:13:47,260
Fifth concubine

280
00:13:47,261 --> 00:13:48,820
is about to be hanged.

281
00:13:50,741 --> 00:13:52,100
What duties are left for you?

282
00:13:53,941 --> 00:13:54,780
Master,

283
00:13:54,821 --> 00:13:56,340
those who betray their masters

284
00:13:56,541 --> 00:13:57,300
must die.

285
00:13:57,301 --> 00:13:58,940
You'll go ahead and wait for her.

286
00:14:00,741 --> 00:14:01,420
Master!

287
00:14:01,461 --> 00:14:02,180
Master, you...

288
00:14:02,261 --> 00:14:02,980
Master!

289
00:14:03,101 --> 00:14:04,780
She is a pitiful soul.

290
00:14:05,021 --> 00:14:05,620
Perhaps...

291
00:14:05,661 --> 00:14:06,300
Master,

292
00:14:06,301 --> 00:14:07,580
just banish her from the estate.

293
